body_text: Hi, I edited the Russian translation because it wasn't quite correct.

fix existing lines to make them more understandable
translate untranslated lines
Add Belarussian translation. Also update Ukrainian and Russian.

I feel like the English (and some formatting) in the README is not as how I would do it, so here are some changes to the @ventoy README. ;)
(Sorry for the ping. We might as well also start translating documentation into other languages, like Spanish.)
The word environment is misspelled at multiple spots
Hi, I added Slovenian Language for Ventoy.

Issues maybe related: #1188 #1658 #2458
I'm testing on a rk3588 sbc with an edk2 firmware.
I encountered the same issue edk2-porting/edk2-rk3588#6 as above.
After a lot of grub_printf I find that file->name here is not initilized by grub_bufio_open. And my rk3588 will get Synchronous Exception when grub_strncmp runs with nullfile->name. So I just skip it when there is no file->name.
